Room.Name: Golden Dolphin Way
Room.ShortDescription: You are walking along Golden Dolphin Way, along the wrong side of the Dentra Central Archery Range, on the north side of the road.
Room.LongDescription: The Dentra Central Archery Range is the finest archery facility in Oceancrest, and perhaps throughout the lands, with the possible exception of some elven ranges. Golden Dolphin Road runs along the rear side of the archery range, where all the targets are. Standing around behind the archery targets is a good way to collect on life insurance.
